{"tid":1559013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【外國勢力系列】【認清現實】香港人正在稍稍地改變世界，得你班撚樣唔知","createTime":"2019-09-10T15:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T07:05:03.000Z","uid":126138,"like":110,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"833064a85b25d9c2a4dcd97f64df7cccdc16cb4e","tid":1559013,"uid":126138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:51:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為香港人，外國人先知原來中國係咁仆街！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外國巴絲做左好多野去令世界鏡頭瞄向香港，但你班撚樣竟然日日玩失敗主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我係上個外國勢力post既樓主，上個post詳見如下:<br />\n<strong>【外國勢力】德國原來勁多人關注香港，連登無人講?</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1551245/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1551245/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我其實有盡睇你地既留言，不過發現好多人都話我自己只係自己打緊飛機。<br />\n我想講，係你地班撚樣太低估自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　<br />\n我詳細少少講下上次8.17漢堡集會後，德國人既迴響:<br />\n<br />\n1. 德國人見到呢單野表示<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>嚇撚親</strong></span>同<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚嬲</span></strong>。<br />\n德國人覺得：明明呢班中國人係德國都係享有民主與自由，點解都可以咁撚樣影人大頭同恐嚇人? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 對華為5G network既關注上升<br />\n德國人本來就好重視私隱。經過呢件事，佢地終於意識到<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國人其實無論係邊都咁仆街</span></strong>架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！對華為呢Ｄ仆街企業都多左關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 對香港了解程度直線上升<br />\n而家人人都分到中國人同香港人啦！以前同外國人講野，人地一定先同你講聲ni hao。想同佢解釋香港同中國既分別，就要慢慢由英殖時期慢慢講。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而家？由中國幾仆街講起就得啦！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n因為香港人，所以外國人終於醒啦！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地知道，中國係一個唔守承諾、鐘意玩監控同經濟滲透既陰險國家</span></span></strong>，比著你係外國人，你仲會唔會同佢玩架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />慢慢睇下中共點含撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明而家香港人好無力、好絕望。<br />\n但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人總不孤單</span></strong></span>。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭是漫漫長路，對手雖強，但正義終會勝利</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港　時代革命<br />\n五大訴求　缺一不可</strong></span>"},{"pid":"cce67a8787259ebc8441c95baf54c882b9ab16db","tid":1559013,"uid":126138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:52:48.000Z","msg":"自推十次，外國巴絲做左咁多野，你地玩失敗主義？你對得住佢地？"},{"pid":"23e8c2e6504742441807f1570c20bd1050d40aea","tid":1559013,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:53:08.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"617704b9f87924e010f8e4ac6744cde40f71345e","tid":1559013,"uid":126138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"全世界望撚住你地呀"},{"pid":"0952da14ec1ca3c5bd2892e020d3d2c23774aba5","tid":1559013,"uid":126138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:53:33.000Z","msg":"咪撚做失敗主義撚"},{"pid":"2b7033751df98e3e4697c42229d4287ce9701060","tid":1559013,"uid":126138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"全世界望撚住你地呀"},{"pid":"8a7b2742a4c